title: Derren.Brown.Infamous.720p.HDTV.x264.W4F
description:
Bafta and RTS-winning Derren Brown presents the extraordinary, acclaimed sell-out stage show Infamous. Featuring his singularly inventive, intelligent mix of thought-provoking, compelling entertainment that leaves his audiences enthralled and enlightened in equal measure. Derren is captured live on stage at the Grand Theatre, Leeds, during his Olivier-nominated tour. The Times described the show as 'a thrilling evening in which Brown offers us the gorgeous idea that we can take control of our own lives while also ensuring that we remain putty in his hands'.


Duration 01:11:04
